## Section 291-2 Reckless driving of vehicle or riding of animals; penalty

[URL](https://sammade.github.io/aloha-io/title-17/chapter-291/section-291-2/)

ยง291-2 Reckless driving of vehicle or riding of animals; penalty. Whoever operates any vehicle or rides any animal recklessly in disregard of the safety of persons or property is guilty of reckless driving of vehicle or reckless riding of an animal, as appropriate, and shall be fined not more than $1,000 or imprisoned not more than thirty days, or both. 

